summary: An Ordinance providing for the condemnation and appropriation of a portion of Tracts Seventy-four (74) and Seventy-fiver (75), West Seattle Five Acre Tracts, Block one (1), Tull's Section Addition to the City of Seattle of West Seattle (now City of Seattle); Block seven (7) and Eight (8) of the Banner Tract, an Addition to West Seattle (now City of Seattle); and a portion of the Southwest Quarter (S.W. 1/4) of the Southeast Quarter (S.E. 1/4) of Section Eleven (11), Township Twenty-four (24) North, Range Three (3) East W. M., all in the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes.
